description:
For sale by Openn Negotiation (flexible conditions online auction). The Openn Negotiation is under way and the property can sell at any time. Contact the sales agent immediately to become qualified and avoid disappointment. Open to all buyers, including finance, subject to seller approval.

PLEASE NOTE - Successful purchaser will have first option to acquire immediate vacant land at 41 South Street Port Albert.)

https://anz.openn.com/app/properties/view/cd4fe89a2geg4re93f60?negotiationId=cd4fe8ha2geg4re93f6g&marketingSite=true

Lovely beachy presented home located in the Historical Coastal town of Port Albert in South Gippsland. If you're looking for a sea escape within the quaint little town and all her charm this is for you! Home is located only a short walk to the water's edge for those lovely strolls in the evening. The home offers views of the water with outdoor area for entertaining upstairs. Inside boasts spacious bedrooms with BIRS in 2 and the Master with en-suite and walk in robe. Family bathroom has separate shower, bath, and toilet. Kitchen/lounge/dining area is accommodating for the large family and guests. Don't forget the concreted powered shed, large enough for the Van and the Boat. Easy maintenance gardens. Property would make a great family home, investment property or holiday home for the family. Port Albert is a premier South Gippsland location.

Vendors want this property sold so get in touch. Call the office on 0351146552 or Ian on 0436036646

For a Due Diligence Checklist go to: consumer.vic.gov.au/duediligencechecklist less
